361
00:23:43,518 --> 00:23:49,083
And it was this early test that made the pitch possible.

362
00:23:50,419 --> 00:23:57,764
Our confidence with the engine allowed us to prove that a single implementer

363
00:23:57,764 --> 00:24:04,849
could essentially pull this whole thing together with little to no animation support.

364
00:24:04,849 --> 00:24:10,833
Resulting in this.

365
00:24:36,972 --> 00:24:41,773
It's all rolling and riding, it's slipping and sliding, it's magic.

366
00:24:41,773 --> 00:24:49,475
