367
00:24:49,475 --> 00:25:02,158
The lesson here is keep yourself honest and prove that your ideas can be accomplished.

368
00:25:02,892 --> 00:25:05,392
preferably by you if possible, because in the end,

369
00:25:05,392 --> 00:25:08,593
you might be the one actually driving the front-end key art.

370
00:25:08,593 --> 00:25:10,933
That's not to say you can't ask for help or pull favors.

