00:25:10,933 --> 00:25:13,753
For example, in the Guardians of the Galaxy key art

372
00:25:13,753 --> 00:25:16,194
I just showed you, it had a professional lighting,

373
00:25:16,194 --> 00:25:18,474
VFX, and animation pass, but we made sure

374
00:25:18,474 --> 00:25:22,695
to keep that work contained, and limited to just polish.

375
00:25:22,695 --> 00:25:24,055
So, we're now at the end of the talk,

